## Status

**MVP (v0.1.0)** — 1 of 5 axes live (Axis 1: Logical Qubit Progress),
3 of 8 gates live (`StaticPointGate`, `SingleSourceCapGate`,
`ThresholdGuard`). See [`CHANGELOG.md`](CHANGELOG.md) for the
post-MVP roadmap.
